{"tid":1857324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國首度證實    第一批武漢台僑約200多人將返台","createTime":"2020-02-02T06:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T07:22:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"42cfec3270f0b181be87d99393af9975d74ae866","tid":1857324,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/02/php24Mkqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F02%2Fphp24Mkqs.jpg&h=e3b2b967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕受新型冠狀病毒影響，中國封鎖嚴重疫區武漢，但當地400多名台灣公民也因此受困，我政府連日以來協商包機撤僑，卻被中方屢屢拖延。如今中國終於首度證實，近日將安排第一批湖北武漢台僑約200多人回台。<br />\n<br />\n據《中新社》報導，湖北省政府台灣事務辦公室（湖北台辦）在當地疫情防控指揮部的統一指揮和國台辦指示下，持續處理台僑返台工作，經過連日來的準備後，首批台僑將在最近幾天搭乘民航包機飛回台灣。<br />\n<br />\n湖北台辦表示，其遵循著「兩岸一家親」的精神並關懷台僑的健康福祉，不僅推出了台胞訊息每日回報的制度，並由湖北台辦系統一對一地聯繫各個台商企業，贈送消毒水、口罩等物資。<br />\n<br />\n湖北台辦說，湖北省的台灣人共有確診病例1起、疑似病例2起，都得到及時的治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3055169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3055169&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9P%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=bd0cc625\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3055169&h=ca9316fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3055169</a>"},{"pid":"5a6176fc9067f520115a70d8f75bd027f2b6edaa","tid":1857324,"uid":12609,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"中國咪你家囉支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699086bdb3658fd678d5b3d6c873a01a85d86db2","tid":1857324,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:39:46.000Z","msg":"班台商會唔會覺得做左人質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114dab0b4ecea6faa1cc94b25e7af4b597